fields.name: Steak Ranchero Burrito
fields.description: A hearty burrito filled with tender steak ranchero, sautéed with tomatoes, onions, and peppers, wrapped in a warm flour tortilla.

fields.name: California Burrito
fields.description: A flavorful California Burrito packed with grilled steak, crispy fries, cheese, sour cream, and guacamole, all wrapped in a warm flour tortilla.

fields.name: Pollo Asado Burrito
fields.description: A delicious Pollo Asado Burrito filled with tender grilled chicken, rice, beans, salsa, and creamy guacamole, wrapped in a warm flour tortilla.

fields.name: Tamal De Pollo
fields.description: Tamale de Pollo is a traditional Latin American dish made of masa (corn dough) filled with seasoned chicken, wrapped in a banana leaf or corn husk, and steamed to perfection.

fields.name: Flan De Caramela
fields.description: Flan de Caramelo is a rich and creamy custard dessert topped with a smooth, golden caramel sauce, offering a perfectly balanced sweetness in every bite.

fields.name: Nachos De Bistec
fields.description: Nachos de Bistec are crispy tortilla chips topped with tender, seasoned steak, melted cheese, and fresh toppings, creating a flavorful and satisfying dish.

fields.name: Torta De Carnitas
fields.description: Tortas de Carnitas are savory Mexican sandwiches made with crispy, tender carnitas, layered on a soft telera or bolillo roll, and topped with fresh garnishes and zesty salsa.

fields.name: Steak Quesadilla
fields.description: A steak quesadilla is a crispy, golden tortilla filled with tender, seasoned steak and melted cheese, creating a flavorful and satisfying bite.

fields.name: Shrimp Burrito
fields.description: A shrimp burrito is a warm flour tortilla filled with succulent, seasoned shrimp, rice, beans, and fresh toppings, wrapped into a flavorful and hearty meal.

fields.name: Burrito De Carnitas
fields.description: A Burrito de Carnitas is a warm flour tortilla stuffed with tender, slow-cooked carnitas, rice, beans, and fresh toppings, wrapped into a delicious and satisfying meal.

fields.name: Fajitas De Pollo
fields.description: Fajitas de pollo is a flavorful Mexican dish featuring marinated, grilled chicken strips served with sautéed bell peppers and onions, typically accompanied by warm tortillas and toppings like salsa, guacamole, and sour cream.

fields.name: Chicken Fajitas Burrito
fields.description: A chicken fajitas burrito is a hearty, flour tortilla wrap filled with seasoned grilled chicken, sautéed bell peppers and onions, rice, beans, and toppings like cheese, sour cream, and salsa.

fields.name: Torta De Pollo
fields.description: A savory Mexican sandwich featuring tender, smoky grilled chicken, creamy avocado, crisp lettuce, ripe tomato, and zesty salsa, all piled into a soft, crusty bolillo roll.
